{
  "info": {
    "name": "IoT充电桩智能运营平台 API",
    "description": "# IoT充电桩智能运营平台 接口测试集合\n\n## 使用说明\n\n1. 导入后先在 Collection Variables 中配置 baseUrl（默认 http://localhost:8080）\n2. 先执行「用户端 > 用户认证 > 用户登录」获取 Token\n3. 登录成功后 Token 会自动存入 Collection 变量 `token`，后续接口自动携带\n4. 管理端接口需要 ADMIN 角色的用户登录后才能访问\n\n## 环境变量\n\n| 变量名 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n|--------|--------|------|\n| baseUrl | http://localhost:8080 | API服务地址 |\n| token | (自动填充) | JWT认证令牌 |\n| orderNo | (自动填充) | 订单编号 |\n\n## 接口分类\n\n- 📱 用户端：注册登录、站点查询、充电控制、订单管理、预约管理\n- 🔧 运营后台：站点管理、充电桩管理、订单管理、计费规则、告警管理、数据统计",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "📱 用户端",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "用户认证",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "用户注册",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                      "    console.log('注册成功:', pm.response.json().data);",
                      "}"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"13800138000\",\n  \"password\": \"123456\",\n  \"nickname\": \"测试用户\"\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/user/register",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "user", "register"]
                },
                "description": "手机号注册新用户。\n\n请求体：\n- phone: 手机号（必填）\n- password: 密码（必填）\n- nickname: 昵称（选填）"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "用户登录",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                      "    const data = pm.response.json().data;",
                      "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', data.token);",
                      "    pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', data.userId);",
                      "    console.log('登录成功, Token已设置');",
                      "}"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"13800138000\",\n  \"password\": \"123456\"\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/user/login",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "user", "login"]
                },
                "description": "手机号+密码登录，成功后自动设置 Collection Token。"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "获取用户信息",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                      "    console.log('用户信息:', pm.response.json().data);",
                      "}"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Authorization",
                    "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
                  }
                ],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/user/info",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "user", "info"]
                },
                "description": "获取当前登录用户的详细信息。需要登录。"
              },
              "response": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "站点查询",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "充电站列表",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                      "    const stations = pm.response.json().data.records;",
                      "    if (stations && stations.length > 0) {",
                      "        pm.collectionVariables.set('stationId', stations[0].id);",
                      "        console.log('站点列表获取成功, 共' + stations.length + '个站点');",
                      "    }",
                      "}"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Authorization",
                    "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
                  }
                ],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/station/list?page=1&size=20&sortBy=price",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "station", "list"],
                  "query": [
                    {"key": "page", "value": "1"},
                    {"key": "size", "value": "20"},
                    {"key": "name", "value": "", "disabled": true},
                    {"key": "sortBy", "value": "price"},
                    {"key": "latitude", "value": "", "disabled": true},
                    {"key": "longitude", "value": "", "disabled": true}
                  ]
                },
                "description": "获取充电站列表，支持分页、排序和名称搜索。\n\n排序方式：\n- price: 按最低电价\n- distance: 按距离（需传经纬度）\n- available: 按空闲桩数"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "充电站详情",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Authorization",
                    "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
                  }
                ],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/station/{{stationId}}",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "station", "{{stationId}}"]
                },
                "description": "获取充电站详细信息及该站下的充电桩列表。"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "充电桩详情",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Authorization",
                    "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
                  }
                ],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/charger/1",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "charger", "1"]
                },
                "description": "获取单个充电桩的详细信息。"
              },
              "response": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "充电控制",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "扫码启桩",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                      "    const orderNo = pm.response.json().data;",
                      "    if (typeof orderNo === 'string') {",
                      "        pm.collectionVariables.set('orderNo', orderNo);",
                      "        console.log('启桩成功, 订单号:', orderNo);",
                      "    } else {",
                      "        // data可能是对象",
                      "        const no = pm.response.json().data.orderNo;",
                      "        if (no) pm.collectionVariables.set('orderNo', no);",
                      "        console.log('启桩成功:', pm.response.json().data);",
                      "    }",
                      "}"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  },
                  {
                    "key": "Authorization",
                    "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"chargerId\": 1\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/charge/start",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "charge", "start"]
                },
                "description": "扫码启动充电。\n\n前置条件：\n- 充电桩状态为「空闲」\n- 充电桩未被其他用户锁定\n\n成功后返回订单编号，自动存入 `orderNo` 变量。"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "充电实时状态",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Authorization",
                    "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
                  }
                ],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/charge/status/{{orderNo}}",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "charge", "status", "{{orderNo}}"]
                },
                "description": "获取充电实时状态：电压、电流、功率、已充电量、实时费用。\n\n使用扫码启桩返回的订单编号。"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "结束充电",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                      "    console.log('充电已结束:', pm.response.json());",
                      "}"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  },
                  {
                    "key": "Authorization",
                    "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"orderNo\": \"{{orderNo}}\"\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/charge/stop",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "charge", "stop"]
                },
                "description": "手动结束当前充电。\n\n成功后会计算费用并生成最终订单。"
              },
              "response": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "订单管理",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "订单列表",
